{"about_the_game":"As a patient at an isolated mental research facility, you will have to prove your skills to survive and make it out alive as gruesome and deranged experiments have gone wrong.<br>Find clues, solve puzzles, hide, and survive in this grizzly first-person survival horror simulator.<br><br><strong>Adapt or Die</strong>...Head Worms takes the player on a horror-filled adventure like no other. Use your skill and wit to navigate indoor and outdoor spaces. Combining different game styles Head Worms keeps players on their toes with a variety of spine-chilling challenges. Do you have what it takes to decipher puzzles and solve riddles while on the run from terrifying creatures? <br><br><strong>Non-static challenges.</strong>..Head Worms offers frequently changing game styles. One moment you could be testing your survival skills fending off a horrifying monster and the next moment you are putting your critical thinking to the test to solve a brain-twisting puzzle in time to avoid certain death.<br><br><strong>Intensity stays high</strong>...While some puzzles may be forgiving on the time allotted to figure them out, other puzzles will require you to be an agile thinker in tense situations.<br><br><strong>Don't get comfortable</strong>...It will take everything you have to survive. Use hiding spots, examine monster patterns, figure out the correct way to solve a puzzle before you try it. Don't get sloppy. The consequences can be fatal.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"puzzle under presure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473930/bf9a21272ea08f2a4ae67d08efcafe165c5d8604.jpg"},{"name":"first encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473930/c9007edeef0fb3897de50ef32c1e9b44c1d27759.jpg"},{"name":"i did not expect that","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473930/5abf77cdbaf10b78df9ccff25c71e1320c19bd08.jpg"},{"name":"noise m